Extract the existing session list rendering from `AgentSidebar.tsx` into a dedicated `SessionsView` component. This is a pure extraction with zero behavioral changes.

## File Location

`apps/client/src/layers/features/session-list/ui/SessionsView.tsx`

## Props Interface

```typescript
